{
  "stem": "16473.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there wasn't any food, as I told you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sick, I had TB.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My parents were trying to find some place where there would be food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just because we were out of the bunker, it didn't mean that there was food around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were eating horses that had been slaughtered in war, that was part of the, you know, food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I know there was a scarcity of food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was severely undernourished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I not only had TB but because of this situation, my whole-- what would I call it-- my female internal organs were affected by this later, a doctor told me so.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were repercussions to this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my parents were trying to get me into a sanitarium, and they were told that if one of them joined the Communist Party and one joined the Socialist Party, by luck of the draw, you know, that would help, either one party or another would help to get me into a sanitarium.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother joined the Communist Party, my dad joined the Socialist Party.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in time, they got a chance for me to go to-- to a sanitarium.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother took me there and I kicked and I screamed at the door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember yelling and screaming, don't leave me, don't leave me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the first night, I slept with a little doll that was given me by a neighbor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was filled with sand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a matchbox and the limbs were filled with sand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I squeezed so hard on that doll that when I woke up in the morning, the whole bed was full of sand and the kids were making fun of me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was tremendously [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] frightened.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
